<div class="py-8 sm:py-12">
  <!-- Header Section -->
  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 sm:gap-6 p-4 text-center mb-8 sm:mb-12">
    <h1 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-2xl sm:text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold leading-tight">
      About Me
    </h1>
    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-base sm:text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto">
      Software engineer building modern web applications with Ruby on Rails.
    </p>
  </div>

  <!-- Content Section -->
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto space-y-6 sm:space-y-8 px-4">
    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#152331] rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-3 sm:mb-4">Background</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-[#92adc9] text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed mb-4">
        I'm a software engineer with 3 years of experience building full-stack web applications with Ruby on Rails.
        In my free time, I love building with AI, leveraging existing models to create practical solutions that solve
        real problems—from intelligent job application tracking to social wishlist platforms with automated product discovery.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-[#92adc9] text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed">
        I've built and deployed personal projects like ApplyTrack and Wishly to explore integrating AI capabilities
        in meaningful ways—conversational interfaces, automated data extraction, and intelligent automation—while
        maintaining solid full-stack development practices with modern Rails and Hotwire.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#152331] rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-3 sm:mb-4">Skills & Technologies</h2>

      <h3 class="text-gray-800 dark:text-primary text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold mb-3 mt-4">Languages & Frameworks</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-primary">▪</span> Ruby on Rails 8
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-primary">▪</span> Hotwire (Turbo & Stimulus)
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-primary">▪</span> Tailwind CSS
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-primary">▪</span> PostgreSQL
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-primary">▪</span> Redis
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-primary">▪</span> AI & LLMs
        </div>
      </div>

      <h3 class="text-gray-800 dark:text-primary text-sm sm:text-base font-semibold mb-3">Deployment & Tools</h3>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-3 gap-3 sm:gap-4">
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-primary">▪</span> Kamal Deployment
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-primary">▪</span> Docker
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-primary">▪</span> Stripe Integration
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-primary">▪</span> Git/GitHub
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-primary">▪</span> RESTful APIs
        </div>
        <div class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300">
          <span class="text-primary">▪</span> Third-party API Integration
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-white dark:bg-[#152331] rounded-xl p-4 sm:p-6 md:p-8 shadow-sm">
      <h2 class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold mb-3 sm:mb-4">Let's Connect</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-[#92adc9] text-sm sm:text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
        I'm always interested in connecting and discussing interesting projects.
        Feel free to reach out if you want to chat about Rails, AI, or anything tech-related!
      </p>
      <%= link_to contact_path, class: "inline-flex h-10 min-w-[120px] cursor-pointer items-center justify-center overflow-hidden rounded-lg bg-primary px-6 text-sm font-bold leading-normal tracking-[0.015em] text-white transition-colors hover:bg-primary/90" do %>
        Get In Touch
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
